title: Kitchen Sink Plug Strainer Stainless Steel Replacement Waste Drainer Stoppper for Food/Hair Waste- UK Sinks Hole Diameter 78mm

Dual Function Strainer and Plug: This new sink strainer plug can be used as a sink plug and sink strainer/filter at the same time. Press the knob dwon to fill sink as sink plug, and lift it slightly to drain the water and collect all the resideues as a strainer.
Easy to Use: Our sink plug strainer is easy to remove and assemble. just follow unscrew the center shaft first, and then assemble the accessories together.
